OL,6,FThe young person at the centre of the
OL,7,Foriginal allegations about Huw Edwards
OL,8,Fhas called for Tim Davie to resign
OL,9,Fover his handling of the presenter's
OL,10,Fscandal
OL,12,FThe BBC has begun wiping archive
OL,13,Ffootage of former broadcaster Huw
OL,14,FEdwards, who pleaded guilty to making
OL,15,Findecent images of children earlier
OL,16,Fthis week, according to reports.
OL,18,FEdwards' image and voice are being
OL,19,Fremoved, starting with family and
OL,20,Fentertainment content on iPlayer, the
OL,21,FObserver reported.
