OL,6,FUntil last year, Edwards was one of
OL,7,Fthe main presenters on BBC One's News
OL,8,Fat Ten and often fronted coverage of
OL,9,Fmajor national events, including the
OL,10,FQueen Elizabeth II's funeral.
OL,12,F"As you would expect we are actively
OL,13,Fconsidering the availability of our
OL,14,Farchive," a BBC spokesperson said.
OL,16,F"While we don't routinely delete
OL,17,Fcontent from the BBC archive as it is
OL,18,Fa matter of historical record, we do
OL,19,Fconsider the continued use and re-use
OL,20,Fof material on a case-by-case basis."
