OL,3,CBBC begins deleting Huw Edwards from
OL,4,Carchive after guilty plea
OL,6,FThe statement comes after Edwards
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to three counts of
OL,8,Fmaking indecent images of children at
OL,9,FWestminster Magistrates Court on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FThe court heard the 62-year-old had
OL,13,Fbeen involved in online chat with an
OL,14,Fadult man on WhatsApp between December
OL,15,F2020 and August 2021, who sent him 377
OL,16,Fsexual images, of which 41 were
OL,17,Findecent images of children.
OL,19,FThe bulk of these, 36, were sent
OL,20,Fduring a two-month period.
