OL,6,FThe indecent images that were sent
OL,7,Fincluded seven category A, the worst,
OL,8,F12 category B, and 22 category C.
OL,10,FOf the category A images, the
OL,11,Festimated age of most of the children
OL,12,Fwas between 13 and 15, but one was
OL,13,Faged between seven and nine, the court
OL,14,Fwas told.
OL,16,FThe final indecent image was sent in
OL,17,FAugust 2021, a category A film
OL,18,Ffeaturing a young boy.
