OL,6,FIn an interview with BBC News, the
OL,7,Fcorporation's director-general was
OL,8,Fquestioned on why he continued to
OL,9,Femploy the veteran broadcaster until
OL,10,FApril, when Edwards resigned on
OL,11,Fmedical advice.
OL,13,F"We knew it was serious, we knew no
OL,14,Fspecifics, apart from the category of
OL,15,Fthe potential offences," Davie
OL,16,Fadmitted.
OL,18,F"The police came to us and said,
OL,19,F'Look, we need to do our work in total
OL,20,Fconfidence, we've arrested, please
OL,21,Fkeep this confidential'.
