OL,9,Fthis, this wasn't a knee-jerk decision.
OL,11,F"And it was difficult but when the
OL,12,Fpolice, if you think about this in
OL,13,Fterms of precedent, people do get
OL,14,Farrested and then we've had situations
OL,15,Fwhere no charges (are made) and
